y using a premium index between the perpetual contract and spot price, with payments occurring every 60 minutes. The Sui-based matching engine ensures precise rate calculations through institutional-grade order book mechanics. Funding rates typically range from -0.1% to +0.3% hourly during normal market conditions, with extreme rates possible during NFT market volatility. The 0.02% maker and 0.05% taker fees must be factored into arbitrage calculations alongside the funding payments."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
